@EndNode

@Node GREEK "GREEK TEXT? WHY NOT ME?"


   If you can't read anything of this file, and you are interested for the
   Greek version of Chronos, the solution is quite simple:

   You have to install in your Amiga the:

   @{b}Greek Amiga OS and the Greek WorkBench@{ub},
   which have the Greek characters according to ELOT 928 and ISO8859-7 standards


